<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sn_aia_agent"><sn_aia_agent action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><description>Biased Categories Selector</description><instructions>You are an audit runner. Follow these steps exactly.
1) Ingest the bias_audit_sys_id from Data Prep Agent and Call tool "Get Bias Audit Data" with received { bias_audit_sys_id }
2) Detect methodology by checking the JSON in dataset_str. - Parse the first object and read its first key. - If the first key is "ai_score" (or "ai score") → method = "Scoring" - If the first key is "status" → method = "Selection"
3) Show methodology used.
4) Use Scoring Methodology tool or Selective Methodology tool based on the choice in step 3 above and then proceed to step 6 with the bias_audit_sys_id.
5) Please ignore {"status":"error","error":"Error: bias_audit_sys_id is required"} error if it pops up and continue on.
6) Use Update the Audit Status tool with the bias_audit_sys_id.
7) Stop.</instructions><internal_name>global.x_snc_ai_complia_0.Biased Categories Selector</internal_name><name>Biased Categories Selector</name><proficiency>- The agent is capable of identifying and selecting biased categories within datasets, ensuring that any potential biases are recognized and addressed. This is central to the agent's function as a 'Biased Categories Selector'. - The agent can retrieve bias audit data using the 'Get Bias Audit Data' tool, which is crucial for initiating the audit process by accessing the necessary dataset. - The agent is capable of detecting the methodology used in the dataset by parsing the JSON structure, which is essential for deciding whether to apply the 'Scoring' or 'Selection' methodology. - The agent can apply the appropriate methodology tool ('Scoring Methodology' or 'Selective Methodology') based on the detected methodology, ensuring the correct approach is used for bias detection. - The agent is capable of updating the audit status using the 'Update the Audit Status' tool, which is essential for completing the audit process and ensuring that the audit results are recorded.</proficiency><record_type>custom</record_type><role>Biased Categories Selector</role><run_as/><strategy display_value="ReAct">f0bff21f9f13c6108f431597d90a1c74</strategy><sys_class_name>sn_aia_agent</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>frants.k</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2025-10-25 22:40:00</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_id>17d9663983b432107f44e8be50da1ec5</sys_id><sys_mod_count>17</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Biased Categories Selector</sys_name><sys_package display_value="AI Compliance Command Center" source="x_snc_ai_complia_0">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="AI Compliance Command Center">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sn_aia_agent_17d9663983b432107f44e8be50da1ec5</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>frants.k</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2025-10-27 01:33:05</sys_updated_on></sn_aia_agent></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sn_aia_tool"><sn_aia_tool action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description>Creates recommended actions requiring user approval for medium-risk changes</description><input_schema>[{"name":"alert_sys_id","description":""},{"name":"risk_level","description":""},{"name":"affected_systems","description":""},{"name":"effective_date","description":""}]</input_schema><name>Generate Approval Actions (Medium Risk)</name><record_type>custom</record_type><script><![CDATA[(function(inputs) {
  var alertSysId = String(inputs.alert_sys_id || '').trim();
  var riskLevel = parseInt(inputs.risk_level || '5');
  var affectedSystemsJson = String(inputs.affected_systems || '[]');
  var effectiveDate = String(inputs.effective_date || '');
  
  gs.info('===== Tool 3: GENERATE APPROVAL ACTIONS =====');
  gs.info('Alert sys_id: ' + alertSysId);
  gs.info('Risk level: ' + riskLevel);
  
  try {
    var affectedSystems = JSON.parse(affectedSystemsJson);
  } catch (e) {
    return {
      actions_created: '0',
      error: 'Invalid JSON input'
    };
  }
  
  var actionsCreated = 0;
  var actionSysIds = [];
  
  // ACTION 1: Trigger Bias Audit via Data Prep Agent
  for (var i = 0; i < affectedSystems.length; i++) {
    var systemName = affectedSystems[i];
    
    // Create recommended action
    var actionGr = new GlideRecord('x_snc_ai_complia_0_recommended_actions_2');
    actionGr.initialize();
    actionGr.setValue('regulatory_alert', alertSysId);
    actionGr.setValue('action_type', 'approval_required');
    actionGr.setValue('action_category', 'process_update');
    actionGr.setValue('action_description', 'Trigger bias audit for ' + systemName + ' via Data Prep Agent');
    actionGr.setValue('risk_level', 'medium');
    actionGr.setValue('status', 'pending');
    actionGr.setValue('requires_approval', true);
    actionGr.setValue('target_agent', 'Data Prep Agent');
    
    // Store parameters for execution after approval
    var params = {
      ai_system_name: systemName,
      audit_type: 'Internal Selection', // Default, user can change
      triggered_by: 'regulatory_change'
    };
    actionGr.setValue('parameters', JSON.stringify(params));
    
    var actionId = actionGr.insert();
    actionSysIds.push(actionId);
    actionsCreated++;
    
    gs.info('Created action: Trigger bias audit for ' + systemName);
  }
  
  // ACTION 2: Update Audit Schedule
  var scheduleActionGr = new GlideRecord('x_snc_ai_complia_0_recommended_actions_2');
  scheduleActionGr.initialize();
  scheduleActionGr.setValue('regulatory_alert', alertSysId);
  scheduleActionGr.setValue('action_type', 'approval_required');
  scheduleActionGr.setValue('action_category', 'process_update');
  scheduleActionGr.setValue('action_description', 'Update audit schedule to quarterly for all affected systems');
  scheduleActionGr.setValue('risk_level', 'medium');
  scheduleActionGr.setValue('status', 'pending');
  scheduleActionGr.setValue('requires_approval', true);
  scheduleActionGr.setValue('target_table', 'x_snc_ai_complia_0_ai_systems');
  
  var scheduleParams = {
    field: 'audit_frequency',
    new_value: 'quarterly',
    affected_systems: affectedSystems
  };
  scheduleActionGr.setValue('parameters', JSON.stringify(scheduleParams));
  
  var scheduleActionId = scheduleActionGr.insert();
  actionSysIds.push(scheduleActionId);
  actionsCreated++;
  
  gs.info('Created action: Update audit schedule');
  
  // Create approval request (simulated - in production, use sn_approval_api)
  var approvalGr = new GlideRecord('sysapproval_approver');
  approvalGr.initialize();
  approvalGr.setValue('source_table', 'x_snc_ai_complia_0_regulatory_alert_2');
  approvalGr.setValue('sysapproval', alertSysId);
  approvalGr.setValue('state', 'requested');
  var approvalId = approvalGr.insert();
  
  // Update alert status
  var alertGr = new GlideRecord('x_snc_ai_complia_0_regulatory_alert_2');
  if (alertGr.get(alertSysId)) {
    alertGr.setValue('status', 'actions_pending');
    alertGr.update();
  }
  
  gs.info('Tool 3: Complete - ' + actionsCreated + ' actions created, awaiting approval');
  
  return {
    actions_created: String(actionsCreated),
    action_sys_ids: JSON.stringify(actionSysIds),
    approval_request_sys_id: approvalId,
    awaiting_approval: 'true'
  };
})(inputs);]]></script><sys_class_name>sn_aia_tool</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>sophia.rafat</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2025-10-30 18:08:04</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_id>6cabd7d783b432107f44e8be50da1ee7</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Generate Approval Actions (Medium Risk)</sys_name><sys_package display_value="AI Compliance Command Center" source="x_snc_ai_complia_0">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="AI Compliance Command Center">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sn_aia_tool_6cabd7d783b432107f44e8be50da1ee7</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>sophia.rafat</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2025-10-30 18:22:54</sys_updated_on><target_document/><target_document_table/><type>script</type></sn_aia_tool></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sn_aia_tool"><sn_aia_tool action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description>Analyzes new regulatory changes and determines risk level and impact</description><input_schema>[{"name":"alert_sys_id","description":""},{"name":"alert_summary","description":""},{"name":"effective_date","description":""},{"name":"source","description":""}]</input_schema><name>Analyze Regulatory Impact</name><record_type>custom</record_type><script><![CDATA[(function(inputs) {
  try {
    gs.info('===== Tool 1: ANALYZE REGULATORY IMPACT =====');
    
    // ===== INPUT VALIDATION =====
    var alertSysId = String(inputs.alert_sys_id || '').trim();
    
    if (!alertSysId) {
      gs.error('Missing required input: alert_sys_id');
      return {
        analysis_success: 'false',
        error: 'Missing required input: alert_sys_id'
      };
    }
    
    gs.info('Processing alert_sys_id: ' + alertSysId);
    
    // ===== GET THE ALERT RECORD =====
    var alertGr = new GlideRecord('x_snc_ai_complia_0_regulatory_alert_2');
    if (!alertGr.get(alertSysId)) {
      gs.error('Regulatory alert not found: ' + alertSysId);
      return {
        analysis_success: 'false',
        error: 'Regulatory alert not found: ' + alertSysId
      };
    }
    
    // ===== READ FROM EXISTING FIELDS =====
    var title = alertGr.getValue('title') || '';
    var summary = alertGr.getValue('summary') || ''; // Your "summary"
    var regulationSource = alertGr.getValue('regulation_source') || ''; // Your "source"
    var effectiveDate = alertGr.getValue('effective_date') || '';
    var documentType = alertGr.getValue('document_type') || '';
    var agencies = alertGr.getValue('agencies') || '';
    var alertNumber = alertGr.getValue('alert_number') || '';
    
    gs.info('Alert details:');
    gs.info('  alert_number: ' + alertNumber);
    gs.info('  title: ' + title.substring(0, 60) + '...');
    gs.info('  abstract length: ' + summary.length);
    gs.info('  regulation_source: ' + regulationSource);
    gs.info('  effective_date: ' + effectiveDate);
    
    if (!summary) {
      gs.error('Alert has no abstract/summary to analyze');
      return {
        analysis_success: 'false',
        error: 'Alert has no abstract/summary to analyze'
      };
    }
    
    // ===== PERFORM ANALYSIS ON THE ABSTRACT =====
    gs.info('Analyzing regulatory text...');
    
    var summaryLower = summary.toLowerCase();
    var titleLower = title.toLowerCase();
    var combinedText = summaryLower + ' ' + titleLower;
    
    // ===== CALCULATE RISK LEVEL (1-10) =====
    var riskLevel = 5; // Start at medium
    
    // HIGH RISK INDICATORS (+3 each)
    if (combinedText.indexOf('mandatory') > -1) {
      riskLevel += 3;
      gs.info('  Risk +3: mandatory requirement');
    }
    if (combinedText.indexOf('immediate') > -1 || combinedText.indexOf('suspend') > -1) {
      riskLevel += 3;
      gs.info('  Risk +3: immediate action/suspension required');
    }
    if (combinedText.indexOf('methodology') > -1 || combinedText.indexOf('threshold') > -1) {
      riskLevel += 3;
      gs.info('  Risk +3: methodology/threshold change');
    }
    if (combinedText.indexOf('penalty') > -1 || combinedText.indexOf('fine') > -1 || combinedText.indexOf('violation') > -1) {
      riskLevel += 2;
      gs.info('  Risk +2: penalties mentioned');
    }
    
    // MEDIUM RISK INDICATORS (+1 each)
    if (combinedText.indexOf('update') > -1 || combinedText.indexOf('revise') > -1) {
      riskLevel += 1;
      gs.info('  Risk +1: update/revision required');
    }
    if (combinedText.indexOf('audit') > -1 && combinedText.indexOf('quarterly') > -1) {
      riskLevel += 2;
      gs.info('  Risk +2: increased audit frequency');
    } else if (combinedText.indexOf('audit') > -1) {
      riskLevel += 1;
      gs.info('  Risk +1: audit requirement');
    }
    
    // LOW RISK INDICATORS (-2 each)
    if (combinedText.indexOf('guidance') > -1 && combinedText.indexOf('mandatory') === -1) {
      riskLevel -= 2;
      gs.info('  Risk -2: guidance only (non-mandatory)');
    }
    if (combinedText.indexOf('extend') > -1 && combinedText.indexOf('deadline') > -1) {
      riskLevel -= 1;
      gs.info('  Risk -1: deadline extension');
    }
    
    // Cap risk level between 1-10
    if (riskLevel > 10) riskLevel = 10;
    if (riskLevel < 1) riskLevel = 1;
    
    gs.info('Calculated risk level: ' + riskLevel + '/10');
    
    // ===== DETERMINE SEVERITY =====
    var severity;
    if (riskLevel >= 7) {
      severity = 'high';
    } else if (riskLevel >= 4) {
      severity = 'medium';
    } else {
      severity = 'low';
    }
    
    gs.info('Severity: ' + severity);
    
    // ===== IDENTIFY IMPACT AREAS =====
    var impactAreas = [];
    
    if (combinedText.indexOf('bias audit') > -1 || combinedText.indexOf('audit') > -1) {
      impactAreas.push('bias_audits');
    }
    if (combinedText.indexOf('ai system') > -1 || combinedText.indexOf('employment decision') > -1) {
      impactAreas.push('ai_systems');
    }
    if (combinedText.indexOf('evidence') > -1 || combinedText.indexOf('documentation') > -1) {
      impactAreas.push('evidence_packs');
    }
    if (combinedText.indexOf('retention') > -1 || combinedText.indexOf('data') > -1) {
      impactAreas.push('data_retention');
    }
    if (combinedText.indexOf('methodology') > -1 || combinedText.indexOf('statistical') > -1) {
      impactAreas.push('statistical_methodology');
    }
    if (combinedText.indexOf('transparency') > -1 || combinedText.indexOf('disclosure') > -1) {
      impactAreas.push('transparency');
    }
    if (combinedText.indexOf('registration') > -1 || combinedText.indexOf('reporting') > -1) {
      impactAreas.push('compliance_reporting');
    }
    
    if (impactAreas.length === 0) {
      impactAreas.push('general_compliance');
    }
    
    gs.info('Impact areas: ' + impactAreas.join(', '));
    
    // ===== IDENTIFY AFFECTED SYSTEMS =====
    var affectedSystems = [];
    
    // Query AI Systems table if it exists
    var aiSystemGr = new GlideRecord('x_snc_ai_complia_0_ai_systems');
    if (aiSystemGr.isValid()) {
      aiSystemGr.addActiveQuery();
      aiSystemGr.query();
      while (aiSystemGr.next()) {
        affectedSystems.push(aiSystemGr.getValue('name'));
      }
      gs.info('Queried AI Systems table: ' + affectedSystems.length + ' systems found');
    } else {
      // Fallback to hardcoded list if table doesn't exist
      affectedSystems = ['Resume Scanner', 'Video Interview Analysis Software (VIAS)', 'Predictive Hiring Tools'];
      gs.info('Using hardcoded AI systems list');
    }
    
    gs.info('Affected systems: ' + affectedSystems.join(', '));
    
    // ===== DETERMINE RECOMMENDED ACTION TYPES =====
    var recommendedActionTypes = [];
    
    if (riskLevel < 4) {
      // LOW RISK: Auto-execute simple data updates
      recommendedActionTypes.push('data_update');
      gs.info('Recommended action: data_update (low risk)');
    } else if (riskLevel >= 4 && riskLevel < 7) {
      // MEDIUM RISK: Require approval for process changes
      recommendedActionTypes.push('process_update');
      recommendedActionTypes.push('trigger_bias_audit');
      gs.info('Recommended actions: process_update, trigger_bias_audit (medium risk)');
    } else {
      // HIGH RISK: Provide manual guidance for policy changes
      recommendedActionTypes.push('policy_update');
      recommendedActionTypes.push('manual_review_required');
      gs.info('Recommended actions: policy_update, manual_review_required (high risk)');
    }
    
    // ===== GENERATE ANALYSIS SUMMARY =====
    var analysisSummary = 'Regulatory change from ' + regulationSource + ' analyzed. ';
    analysisSummary += 'Risk Level: ' + riskLevel + '/10 (' + severity + '). ';
    analysisSummary += 'Impact areas: ' + impactAreas.join(', ') + '. ';
    analysisSummary += 'Affected systems: ' + affectedSystems.join(', ') + '. ';
    if (effectiveDate) {
      analysisSummary += 'Effective date: ' + effectiveDate + '. ';
    }
    analysisSummary += 'Recommended actions: ';
    if (riskLevel < 4) {
      analysisSummary += 'Auto-execute data updates.';
    } else if (riskLevel >= 4 && riskLevel < 7) {
      analysisSummary += 'Approval required for process updates and bias audits.';
    } else {
      analysisSummary += 'Manual review and policy guidance required.';
    }
    
    gs.info('Analysis summary created');
    
    // ===== WRITE TO NEW FIELDS =====
    gs.info('Updating alert record with analysis results...');
    
    alertGr.setValue('risk_level', riskLevel);
    alertGr.setValue('severity', severity);
    alertGr.setValue('impact_areas', impactAreas.join(','));
    alertGr.setValue('affected_systems', affectedSystems.join(','));
    alertGr.setValue('analysis_summary', analysisSummary);
    alertGr.setValue('status', 'analyzed');
    alertGr.setValue('analysis_completed_date', new GlideDateTime().getValue());
    alertGr.setValue('created_by_agent', 'Regulatory Analyzer Agent');
    
    var updateResult = alertGr.update();
    
    if (!updateResult) {
      gs.error('Failed to update alert record');
      return {
        analysis_success: 'false',
        error: 'Failed to update alert record'
      };
    }
    
    gs.info('✓ Alert record updated successfully');
    gs.info('===== Tool 1: COMPLETE =====');
    
    // ===== RETURN RESULTS =====
    return {
      analysis_success: 'true',
      alert_sys_id: alertSysId,
      alert_number: alertNumber,
      risk_level: String(riskLevel),
      severity: severity,
      impact_areas: JSON.stringify(impactAreas),
      affected_systems: JSON.stringify(affectedSystems),
      analysis_summary: analysisSummary,
      recommended_action_types: JSON.stringify(recommendedActionTypes)
    };
    
  } catch (e) {
    gs.error('===== Tool 1 ERROR =====');
    gs.error('Error: ' + e.message);
    gs.error('Stack: ' + e.stack);
    
    return {
      analysis_success: 'false',
      error: e.name + ': ' + e.message
    };
  }
})(inputs);]]></script><sys_class_name>sn_aia_tool</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>sophia.rafat</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2025-10-30 18:08:03</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_id>54abd7d783b432107f44e8be50da1eb7</sys_id><sys_mod_count>3</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Analyze Regulatory Impact</sys_name><sys_package display_value="AI Compliance Command Center" source="x_snc_ai_complia_0">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="AI Compliance Command Center">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sn_aia_tool_54abd7d783b432107f44e8be50da1eb7</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>sophia.rafat</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2025-10-30 19:18:41</sys_updated_on><target_document/><target_document_table>undefined</target_document_table><type>script</type></sn_aia_tool></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sysauto_script"><sysauto_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><business_calendar/><condition/><conditional>false</conditional><entered_time>1970-01-01 00:00:00</entered_time><max_drift/><name>EU Regulatory Alerts Fetcher</name><offset/><offset_type>0</offset_type><run_as display_value="Sophia Rafat">65f7855583f032107f44e8be50da1eba</run_as><run_as_tz/><run_dayofmonth>1</run_dayofmonth><run_dayofweek>1</run_dayofweek><run_period/><run_start>2025-10-31 03:28:36</run_start><run_time>1970-01-01 00:00:00</run_time><run_type>on_demand</run_type><script><![CDATA[
(function() {
    var CLOUD_RUN_URL = 'https://ac3-eu-fetcher-641778144701.us-central1.run.app'; 
    
     try {
        gs.info('Fetching EU regulatory data from Cloud Run...');
        
        // Call Cloud Run service
        var rest = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2();
        rest.setHttpMethod('GET');
        rest.setEndpoint(CLOUD_RUN_URL + '/api/eu-regulations');
        rest.setQueryParameter('since', '365d');
        rest.setQueryParameter('minScore', '60');
        rest.setHttpTimeout(30000);
        
        var response = rest.execute();
        
        if (response.getStatusCode() != 200) {
            gs.error('Cloud Run error: ' + response.getStatusCode());
            return;
        }
        
        var data = JSON.parse(response.getBody());
        
        if (!data.success) {
            gs.error('Cloud Run returned error: ' + data.message);
            return;
        }
        
        var alertsCreated = 0;
        
        // Map each result to Regulatory Alerts table
        for (var i = 0; i < data.results.length; i++) {
            var reg = data.results[i];
            
            try {
                // Check if alert already exists (by source_url to prevent duplicates)
                var existing = new GlideRecord('x_snc_ai_complia_0_regulatory_alert_2');
                existing.addQuery('source_url', reg.url);
                existing.query();
                
                if (!existing.next()) {
                    // Create new alert - CORRECT TABLE NAME
                    var alert = new GlideRecord('x_snc_ai_complia_0_regulatory_alert_2');
                    alert.title = reg.title;
                    alert.abstract = reg.description;
                    alert.document_number = reg.celexId;
                    alert.publication_date = reg.pubDate;
                    alert.effective_date = reg.pubDate; // Using pubDate as fallback
                    alert.source_url = reg.url;
                    alert.regulation_source = 'EU';
                    alert.document_type = reg.docType;
                    alert.agencies = reg.trackedLaw || 'EU Commission';
                    
                    alert.insert();
                    alertsCreated++;
                    gs.info('Created alert: ' + reg.title);
                }
            } catch (e) {
                gs.error('Error processing regulation: ' + e.message);
            }
        }
        
        gs.info('Successfully created ' + alertsCreated + ' new EU regulatory alerts');
        
    } catch (e) {
        gs.error('Error: ' + e.message);
    }
})();]]></script><sys_class_name>sysauto_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>sophia.rafat</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2025-10-31 03:29:40</sys_created_on><sys_id>abeb5da3837872107f44e8be50da1ee6</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>EU Regulatory Alerts Fetcher</sys_name><sys_package display_value="AI Compliance Command Center" source="x_snc_ai_complia_0">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="AI Compliance Command Center">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sysauto_script_abeb5da3837872107f44e8be50da1ee6</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>sophia.rafat</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2025-10-31 03:45:09</sys_updated_on><time_zone/><upgrade_safe>false</upgrade_safe></sysauto_script></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sn_aia_tool"><sn_aia_tool action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description>Retrieves all applicant records filtered by the specified AI system for bias audit processing. Returns all matching records as a JSON array string.</description><input_schema>[{"name":"ai_system_name","description":"{{ai_system_name}}"}]</input_schema><name>Query Applicants by AI System</name><record_type>custom</record_type><script><![CDATA[(function(inputs) {
  var TBL = 'x_snc_ai_complia_0_applicants';
  var AI_SYSTEM = String(inputs.ai_system_name || '').trim();
  
  gs.info('Tool 1: Querying applicants for ai_system name: "' + AI_SYSTEM + '"');
  
  if (!AI_SYSTEM) {
    return {
      applicant_records_ndjson_blob: '',
      total_records: '0',
      query_status: 'error',
      error_message: 'Missing AI system name'
    };
  }
  
  var gr = new GlideRecord(TBL);
  gr.addQuery('ai_system', AI_SYSTEM);
  gr.query();
  
  var rowCount = gr.getRowCount();
  gs.info('Tool 1: Found ' + rowCount + ' applicant records');
  
  var rows = [];
  while (gr.next()) {
    var hispVal = gr.getValue('hispanic_or_latino');
    var hispBool = (hispVal === 'true' || hispVal === '1' || hispVal === true || hispVal === 1);
    
    // Build anonymized row - NO sys_id included
    var row = {
      sex: String(gr.getValue('sex') || ''),
      race: String(gr.getValue('race') || ''),
      hispanic_or_latino: hispBool,
      status: String(gr.getValue('status') || ''),
      ai_score: parseFloat(gr.getValue('ai_score') || 0)
    };
    rows.push(row);
  }
  
  var lines = [];
  for (var i = 0; i < rows.length; i++) {
    lines.push(JSON.stringify(rows[i]));
  }
  
  return {
    applicant_records_ndjson_blob: lines.join('\n'),
    total_records: String(rows.length),
    query_status: 'success'
  };
})(inputs);]]></script><sys_class_name>sn_aia_tool</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>frants.k</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2025-10-25 22:39:37</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_id>2dd966f583b432107f44e8be50da1e40</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Query Applicants by AI System</sys_name><sys_package display_value="AI Compliance Command Center" source="x_snc_ai_complia_0">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="AI Compliance Command Center">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sn_aia_tool_2dd966f583b432107f44e8be50da1e40</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>frants.k</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2025-10-27 01:11:36</sys_updated_on><target_document/><target_document_table/><type>script</type></sn_aia_tool></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sn_aia_tool"><sn_aia_tool action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description>Create a record on the Evidence Pack table and Update Bias Audit record</description><input_schema>[{"name":"bias_audit_sys_id","description":"{{Tool 3.bias_audit_sys_id}}"}]</input_schema><name>Create Evidence Pack and Update Bias Audit</name><record_type>custom</record_type><script><![CDATA[(function(inputs) {
  var biasAuditSysId = String(inputs.bias_audit_sys_id || '').trim();
  
  gs.info('===== Tool 4: CREATE EVIDENCE PACK AND UPDATE =====');
  gs.info('Input bias_audit_sys_id: ' + biasAuditSysId);
  
  if (!biasAuditSysId) {
    gs.error('Tool 4: Missing bias_audit_sys_id');
    return {
      success: 'false',
      error: 'Missing bias_audit_sys_id from Tool 3'
    };
  }
  
  // Create Evidence Pack
  gs.info('Tool 4: Creating Evidence Pack...');
  var epGr = new GlideRecord('x_snc_ai_complia_0_evidence_pack');
  epGr.initialize();
  var epSysId = epGr.insert();
  
  if (!epSysId) {
    gs.error('Tool 4: Failed to create Evidence Pack');
    return {
      success: 'false',
      error: 'Failed to create Evidence Pack record'
    };
  }
  
  gs.info('Tool 4: Created Evidence Pack sys_id: ' + epSysId);
  
  // Get the auto-generated number for reporting
  var epLookup = new GlideRecord('x_snc_ai_complia_0_evidence_pack');
  if (!epLookup.get(epSysId)) {
    gs.error('Tool 4: Could not retrieve Evidence Pack after creation');
    return {
      success: 'false',
      error: 'Created Evidence Pack but could not retrieve it'
    };
  }
  
  var evidenceNumber = epLookup.getValue('number');
  gs.info('Tool 4: Evidence Pack number: ' + evidenceNumber);
  
  // Update Bias Audit with Evidence Pack REFERENCE (sys_id, not number)
  gs.info('Tool 4: Looking up Bias Audit: ' + biasAuditSysId);
  var baGr = new GlideRecord('x_snc_ai_complia_0_bias_audits');
  if (!baGr.get(biasAuditSysId)) {
    gs.error('Tool 4: Bias Audit not found: ' + biasAuditSysId);
    return {
      success: 'false',
      error: 'Bias Audit record not found: ' + biasAuditSysId
    };
  }
  
  gs.info('Tool 4: Found Bias Audit record');
  gs.info('Tool 4: Setting evidence reference to Evidence Pack sys_id: ' + epSysId);
  
  // Set the reference field to the Evidence Pack sys_id
  baGr.setValue('evidence', epSysId);
  
  var updateResult = baGr.update();
  gs.info('Tool 4: Update returned: ' + updateResult);
  
  if (!updateResult) {
    gs.error('Tool 4: Update operation returned false');
    return {
      success: 'false',
      error: 'Update operation failed - check ACLs and business rules'
    };
  }
  
  // Verify the update worked
  var verifyGr = new GlideRecord('x_snc_ai_complia_0_bias_audits');
  if (verifyGr.get(biasAuditSysId)) {
    var finalValue = verifyGr.getValue('evidence');
    gs.info('Tool 4: Final evidence reference value: ' + finalValue);
    gs.info('Tool 4: Evidence display value: ' + verifyGr.getDisplayValue('evidence'));
  }
  
  gs.info('Tool 4: SUCCESS - Linked Evidence Pack ' + evidenceNumber + ' to Bias Audit');
  
  return {
    success: 'true',
    evidence_pack_sys_id: epSysId,
    evidence_number: evidenceNumber,
    bias_audit_sys_id: biasAuditSysId
  };
})(inputs);]]></script><sys_class_name>sn_aia_tool</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>frants.k</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2025-10-25 22:39:38</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_id>e5d9263983b432107f44e8be50da1eae</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Create Evidence Pack and Update Bias Audit</sys_name><sys_package display_value="AI Compliance Command Center" source="x_snc_ai_complia_0">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="AI Compliance Command Center">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sn_aia_tool_e5d9263983b432107f44e8be50da1eae</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>frants.k</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2025-10-27 01:11:36</sys_updated_on><target_document/><target_document_table/><type>script</type></sn_aia_tool></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sn_aia_tool_acabd7d783b432107f44e8be50da1ec8
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sn_aia_tool"><sn_aia_tool action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description>Executes actions after user approval via workflow</description><input_schema>[{"name":"action_sys_id","description":""}]</input_schema><name>Execute Approved Actions</name><record_type>custom</record_type><script><![CDATA[(function(inputs) {
  var actionSysId = String(inputs.action_sys_id || '').trim();
  
  gs.info('===== Tool 4: EXECUTE APPROVED ACTION =====');
  gs.info('Action sys_id: ' + actionSysId);
  
  // Get the action record
  var actionGr = new GlideRecord('x_snc_ai_complia_0_recommended_actions_2');
  if (!actionGr.get(actionSysId)) {
    return {
      success: 'false',
      error: 'Action not found'
    };
  }
  
  // Verify it's approved
  if (actionGr.getValue('status') !== 'approved') {
    return {
      success: 'false',
      error: 'Action not approved'
    };
  }
  
  var actionDescription = actionGr.getValue('action_description');
  var targetAgent = actionGr.getValue('target_agent');
  var parametersJson = actionGr.getValue('parameters');
  
  var executionResult = 'success';
  
  try {
    var parameters = JSON.parse(parametersJson);
    
    // If target is Data Prep Agent, trigger it
    if (targetAgent === 'Data Prep Agent') {
      gs.info('Triggering Data Prep Agent with parameters: ' + parametersJson);
      
      // In production, use actual agent API
      // var agent = new sn_agent.Agent('Data Prep Agent');
      // agent.execute(parameters);
      
      // For now, simulate by logging
      gs.info('Would trigger Data Prep Agent for system: ' + parameters.ai_system_name);
      gs.info('Audit type: ' + parameters.audit_type);
      
    } else {
      // Update database directly
      var targetTable = actionGr.getValue('target_table');
      
      if (targetTable && parameters.field && parameters.new_value) {
        for (var i = 0; i < parameters.affected_systems.length; i++) {
          var systemName = parameters.affected_systems[i];
          
          var updateGr = new GlideRecord(targetTable);
          updateGr.addQuery('name', systemName);
          updateGr.query();
          
          if (updateGr.next()) {
            updateGr.setValue(parameters.field, parameters.new_value);
            updateGr.update();
            gs.info('Updated ' + systemName + ': ' + parameters.field + ' = ' + parameters.new_value);
          }
        }
      }
    }
    
  } catch (e) {
    gs.error('Execution failed: ' + e.message);
    executionResult = 'failed: ' + e.message;
  }
  
  // Update action status
  actionGr.setValue('status', 'executed');
  actionGr.setValue('executed_date', new GlideDateTime().getValue());
  actionGr.setValue('execution_result', executionResult);
  actionGr.update();
  
  gs.info('Tool 4: Action executed successfully');
  
  return {
    success: 'true',
    execution_result: executionResult,
    action_description: actionDescription
  };
})(inputs);]]></script><sys_class_name>sn_aia_tool</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>sophia.rafat</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2025-10-30 18:08:04</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_id>acabd7d783b432107f44e8be50da1ec8</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Execute Approved Actions</sys_name><sys_package display_value="AI Compliance Command Center" source="x_snc_ai_complia_0">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="AI Compliance Command Center">7a91febe83a032107f44e8be50da1e4b</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sn_aia_tool_acabd7d783b432107f44e8be50da1ec8</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>sophia.rafat</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2025-10-30 18:18:03</sys_updated_on><target_document/><target_document_table/><type>script</type></sn_aia_tool></record_update>
